\c 18
\s Shoko remuumbi wehari
\p
\v 1 Shoko rakasvika kuna Jeremiya kubva kuna Jehovha, richiti:
\v 2 Simuka, uburukire kuimba yemuumbi; zvino ipapo ndichakunzwisa mashoko angu.
\v 3 Zvino ndakaburukira kuimba yemuumbi wehari, zvino tarira, waiita basa pamavhiri.
\v 4 Zvino mudziyo waaiita waiva washatiswa muruoko rwemuumbi, zvino akaita nayo umwe mudziyo, sezvaiva zvakanaka pameso emuumbi kuita.
\v 5 Zvino shoko raJehovha rakasvika kwandiri richiti:
\v 6 Imba yaIsraeri, handingaiiti kwamuri se\add zvaita\add* ruoko rwemuumbi uyu here? Anoreva Jehovha: Tarira, seivhu riri muruoko rwemuumbi, \add ma\add*kadaro muruoko rwangu, imwi imba yaIsraeri.
\v 7 Nechinguvana ndichataura maererano nerudzi, uye pamusoro peushe, kurudzura, nekuruputsa, nekuruparadza;
\v 8 kana rudzi urwo, rwandataura kururwisa rwukatendeuka pauipi hwarwo, ndichazvidemba pamusoro pechakaipa chandinofunga kuvaitira.
\v 9 Uye nechinguvana ndichataura maererano nerudzi, uye maererano neushe, kuvaka neku\add rwu\add*sima;
\v 10 kana rwukaita chakaipa pameso angu, kuti rwusateerera kuinzwi rangu, ipapo ndichazvidemba pane zvakanaka zvandakati ndichavaitira.
\p
\v 11 Naizvozvo ikozvino, taura hako nevanhu vaJudha nevagari veJerusarema, uti: Anoreva seizvi Jehovha: Tarira, ndinokuvakira zvakaipa, ndinokurongera zano, dzokai ikozvino umwe neumwe panzira yake yakaipa, uye muite nzira dzenyu nezviito zvenyu zvive zvakanaka.
\v 12 Asi ivo vakati: Hapana tariro, asi tichafamba tichitevera mazano edu, uye tichaita umwe neumwe murangariro wemoyo wake wakaipa.
\v 13 Naizvozvo anoreva seizvi Jehovha: Bvunzai imwi pakati pevahedheni, ndiyani wakambonzwa zvinhu zvakadaro, mhandara dzekwaIsraeri dzakaita chinhu chinotyisa zvikuru.
\v 14 \add Munhu\add* angasiya magada echando eRebhanoni anobva paibwe remusango here? Mvura inotonhora, inoyerera ichibva kure ingasiiwa here?
\v 15 Nokuti vanhu vangu vakandikanganwa, vakapisira vamwari venhema zvipfungaidzo zvinonhuhwira; uye vakazvigumbusa panzira dzavo, makwara ekare, kuti vafambe nedzinzira, nzira isina kusimudzirwa.
\v 16 Kuti vaite nyika yavo dongo, kuridzirwa murudzo nekusingaperi; umwe neumwe unopfuurapo achashamiswa, uye achadzungudza musoro wake.
\v 17 Ndichavaparadzira \add se\add*mhepo yekumabvazuva pamberi pemuvengi; ndichavaratidza musana, uye kwete chiso, pazuva redambudziko.
\p
\v 18 Zvino vakati: Uyai, timurangane mazano Jeremiya; nokuti murairo haungaparari kubva kumupristi, nekuraira kubva kune vakachenjera, kana shoko kubva kumuporofita. Uyai ngatimurove nerurimi, uye ngatisateerera kune ripi neripi remashoko ake.
\p
\v 19 Ndirangarirei JehovhaJehovha, zvino muteerere kuinzwi revanondikakavadza.
\v 20 Chakaipa chinotsiviwa nechakanaka here? Nokuti vacherera mweya wangu gomba. Rangarirai kuti ndakamira pamberi penyu kutaura zvakanaka pamusoro pavo, kuti mutsause kutsamwa kwenyu kubva kwavari.
\v 21 Naizvozvo ipai vana vavo kunzara, uye mudurure ropa ravo nesimba remunondo, uye vakadzi vavo ngavafirwe nevana vavo, uye vave chirikadzi, zvino varume vavo ngavaSaka sundirai vana vavo panzara, muvaregere pasimba romunondo; vakadzi vavo ngavatorerwe vana vavo, vave chirikadzi; varume vavo ngavaurawe, majaya avo achaurawa nemunondo pahondo.
\v 22 Kuchema ngakunzwikwe padzimba dzavo, pamuchauisa pakarepo boka revarwi pamusoro pavo, nokuti vakachera gomba kunditora, nekuvanzira tsoka dzangu misungo.
\v 23 Zvakadaro imwi Jehovha munoziva mazano avo ese vachindirwisa ku\add ndi\add*uraya, musaregerera kuipa kwao, kana kudzima chivi chavo kubva pachiso chenyu, asi ngavapidigurwe pamberi penyu, batai navo panguva yekutsamwa kwenyu.